data.description: Have you been looking for a MOVE IN READY townhome in Riverdale? If so, this is a home you need to see! A few features include: END UNIT located near guest parking, 2 large bedrooms,  updated paint, covered patio, carport & more! This community offers a swimming pool, RV parking, and more. You are within minutes of freeway access, all major shopping, walking trails & more. The seller will even cover the new buyer's HOA fees for a year at closing! Call today for a private tour; you'll be glad you did!
